favourites.title: Investor bets shift as dollar weakens with looming Fed rate cuts - Reuters
favourites.description: The U.S. dollar's decline is gaining speed as anticipated interest rate cuts by the Federal Reserve threaten to end the greenback's years-long period of strength.
